# 🧩 Chunk Selection

The manager scans world bounds:

```gdscript
for x in range(min,max)
for y in range(min,max)
```

Each chunk receives:

* Grid position
* Distance from player
* LOD level

---

# 🎯 LOD Selection

Current logic:

```text
Distance <= Load Radius
        |
        v
       LOD0

Distance <= LOD1 Range
        |
        v
       LOD1

Distance <= LOD2 Range
        |
        v
       LOD2
```

---

