---

# 🔁 LOD Replacement

Only one LOD version of a chunk exists at a time.

Example:

Before:

```
0_0_LOD1
```

Player approaches:

```
0_0_LOD0
```

Manager removes:

```
0_0_LOD1
```

and replaces it.

